    {
      "id": 67080,
      "category": "researcher",
      "content": "Semrush has a microservices architecture, there is an API gateway which routes to the server corresponding to the service in the internal network. Some Semrush services use spring boot with actuator endpoints enabled, some services left these endpoints publicly accessible. It was therefore possible to access it as follow: https://semrush.com/service-xyz/actuator/ . Some endpoints leaked sensitive internal data.",
